#12171
Name Eastern Alcove~
Desc This small alcove is clearly set up as a sleeping area.  A comfortable 
looking bed, a small table and chair, and a basin of cool, clear water are 
here.  There is also a chest containing several wool blankets if the heat 
from the fire pit is not enough.  Two unlit torches are in sconces on the 
wall.  The appear unneeded as the glow from the fire lights this area quite 
well. 
~
