#12175
Name Master's Room~
Desc Oppulence is not the first word that comes to mind upon viewing this room. 
The contents are sparse, but upon closer inspection are made of the finest 
materials and workmanship.  `1`1A fireplace is set in the middle of the north wall and a large posted bed 
is off to the east side.  Thick carpets made of animal furs cover the floor 
and a large map of the Realms is on the west wall.  On the south wall, next 
to the door, is a large display rack holding a multitude of axes of all 
shapes, sizes, and designs.  Obviously the owner is a collector, and is 
quite proud of his results.  A chest seems built in to the wall near the 
bed.  It has a huge and very complicated lock on it. 
~
