#12177
Name Storage Room~
Desc This room is full of boxes, crates, bags, pouches, sacks, bushels, 
baskets...  containers of all kinds.  They are packed in here seemingly in 
no order.  The walls are lined with shelves and they are crammed full. Dried 
goods dominate the contents - flour, corn meal, sugar, barley, salt, pepper 
and other spices...  even nuts are found in here.  Narrow pathways are left 
clear to reach the far corners of the room.  A trapdoor leading to stairs 
down is in the center of the floor. 
~
